data.description: Price reduced!!! Welcome to your beautiful single-family home in the Spanish Gate Village community of Timber Oaks. The mature landscaping and lovely gardens in the front welcome you right in. Upon entering the split floorplan, you have a spacious bedroom to the right. The living dining area offers plenty of room to entertain. The galley style kitchen has ample storage with built in pantry. It also has a pull-out table for dining. The primary bedroom features an En suite bathroom with standalone shower. The enclosed porch that is fully air conditioned is the perfect space to have an office or den. To the right of the enclosed porch, there is a large room that could be used for entertainment or a third bedroom. This home also has polycarbonate hurricane sheeting on the back and side windows and is not located in a flood zone. Spanish Gate Village has it's own private pool. Timber Oaks is a Deed Restricted 55+ community known for it's clubhouse, pool and tennis courts. Shopping and dining nearby. Conveniently located right off SR52.
